---
import BaseLayout from "src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "About This Blog | LoneVoice.in";
const description = "Learn about us | LoneVoice.in";
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
    <main class="wrapper py-6 md:py-8 lg:py-10">
        <div class="typography">
            <h1 class="heading text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl">
                About This Blog
            </h1>
            <p>
                This is my humble attempt at being a blogger, writing about
                topics i find interesting and wish to spread those ideas and
                information into the world.
            </p>
            <p>
                I believe in the power of knowledge and dialogue to drive
                positive change. Through well-researched articles and thoughtful
                analysis, i aim to shed light on pressing issues facing our
                society today, from economic inequalities to political reforms.
                i hope to provide a platform for informed discussion on the
                critical issues of our time. I strive to present complex topics
                in a way that is accessible to a broad audience, encouraging
                critical thinking and intellectual engagement.
            </p>
            <p>
                I hope you find the blog a joy to read and tickles your
                intellectual curiosity. Please <a href="/contact/">contact me</a
                > if you have something to articulate. Thank you for being a part
                of my community.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
